# NAME: Apple System Update Block
# AUTHOR: Minis
# REPO: https://github.com/Aioneas/Surge
# UPDATED: 2026-05-03
# NOTES: Block Apple software update check & download domains.
#        Synced from /etc/hosts block list on Mac.
#        This prevents macOS/iOS from discovering or downloading system updates.
#
# --- Software Update catalog & download ---
DOMAIN,swscan.apple.com
DOMAIN,swdist.apple.com
DOMAIN,swdownload.apple.com
DOMAIN,swcdn.apple.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,swscan.apple.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,swdist.apple.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,swdownload.apple.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,swcdn.apple.com
# --- CDN for update payloads / MobileAsset wallpapers ---
# NOTE: Do NOT block updates-http.cdn-apple.com or updates.cdn-apple.com.
# macOS wallpaper / MobileAsset downloads use these CDN hosts; system update
# discovery is still blocked by swscan/swdist/swdownload/swcdn/gdmf/oscdn/etc.
# DOMAIN,updates-http.cdn-apple.com     # 暂不屏蔽：壁纸/MobileAsset 下载需要此域名
# DOMAIN,updates.cdn-apple.com          # 暂不屏蔽：壁纸下载需要此域名
# DOMAIN-SUFFIX,updates-http.cdn-apple.com # 同上
# DOMAIN-SUFFIX,updates.cdn-apple.com   # 同上
# --- Device management / update metadata ---
DOMAIN,gdmf.apple.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,gdmf.apple.com
# --- Update experience / telemetry ---
DOMAIN,xp.apple.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,xp.apple.com
# --- MobileAsset catalog ---
# NOTE: Do NOT block mesu.apple.com globally. macOS Wallpaper/MobileAsset also
# queries mesu.apple.com for asset catalogs. System update discovery/download
# remains blocked by swscan/swdist/swdownload/swcdn/gdmf/oscdn/etc.
# DOMAIN,mesu.apple.com                # 暂不屏蔽：壁纸/MobileAsset 目录需要
# DOMAIN-SUFFIX,mesu.apple.com         # 同上
# --- Software lookup / update service ---
DOMAIN,gsp64-ssl.ls.apple.com
# --- Additional OTA update domains ---
DOMAIN,oscdn.apple.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,oscdn.apple.com
DOMAIN,osrecovery.apple.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,osrecovery.apple.com
DOMAIN,gg.apple.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,gg.apple.com
DOMAIN,ns.itunes.apple.com
DOMAIN,appldnld.apple.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,appldnld.apple.com
